  <div class="col-12">
    <h2 id="intro">About</h2>
    <p> 
    This site is a logical extention to <a href="https://pgexercises.com/">PG Exercises </a>
    While there are several websites similar to PG Exercises that allow you to interact with SQL interactivly
    none of them focus on the post sql-92 window functions. Most databases got these awesome powerfull functions
    a long time ago and most of us don't use them
    </p>
