    </p> 
    <p> Made with love at <a href="https://www.recurse.com"> Recurse Center</a>

    <p> Links to learn about window functions: 
    <a href="https://community.modeanalytics.com/sql/tutorial/sql-window-functions/">Modeanalytics</a>
